00:08:33.081 --> 00:08:37.970
like this, psi j.

00:08:37.970 --> 00:08:42.490
And now, remember q is an
eigenvalue for Hermitian

00:08:42.490 --> 00:08:43.570
operator.

00:08:43.570 --> 00:08:45.320
We already know it's real.

00:08:45.320 --> 00:08:49.890
So q goes out of the
